title: Altagracia Contreras
summary: Altagracia Contreras (born 18 February 1974) is a Dominican Republic judoka. She competed in the women's lightweight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics.
content:
Altagracia Contreras (born 18 February 1974) is a Dominican Republic judoka. She competed in the women's lightweight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics.
